---
title: Lemon-Caper Grilled Salmon with Asparagus, Zucchini and Potatoes
description: An elegant fish feast, on the grill! Foil-pouch potatoes and a sheet of foil under the salmon make clean-up a breeze. More time to enjoy the outdoors!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saumon-grille-au-citron-et-aux-capres-c2ff1fa1.jpg
